OL,3,C'I just think of Rita': Man climbs Pen
OL,4,Cy Fan over 600 times in wife's memory
OL,6,FITV News Wales reporter Rhys Williams
OL,7,Ftalks to Chris Daniels, who has
OL,8,Fclimbed the highest peak in South
OL,9,FWales, Pen y Fan, 600 times in honour
OL,10,Fof his late wife
OL,12,FIf you've climbed Pen y Fan over the
OL,13,Flast year or so, you've probably seen
OL,14,FChris Daniels.
OL,16,FThe 62-year-old grandfather has
OL,17,Freached the summit of the highest peak
OL,18,Fin Bannau Brycheiniog more than 600
OL,19,Ftimes since April, often climbing it
OL,20,Fmultiple times a day.
