OL,3,C'I just think of Rita': Man climbs Pen
OL,4,Cy Fan over 600 times in wife's memory
OL,6,F"We met when we were 17. We were
OL,7,Falways together. She was so full of
OL,8,Flife, she had so much to live for. And
OL,9,FI've got grandchildren now, and she
OL,10,Fwould have been an amazing
OL,11,Fgrandmother."
OL,13,F"Knowing what she went through makes
OL,14,Fwhat I'm going through on even the
OL,15,Fworst days relatively easy," he adds.
OL,17,F"That keeps me focused and pushes me
OL,18,Fon."
