OL,3,C'I just think of Rita': Man climbs Pen
OL,4,Cy Fan over 600 times in wife's memory
OL,6,FToday is one of those days. The rain
OL,7,Fis relentless, the wind lashes your
OL,8,Fface, and the temperature at the
OL,9,Fsummit is well below freezing. Still,
OL,10,FChris keeps moving.
OL,12,F"These conditions are absolutely
OL,13,Fhorrible," he admits. "It's so easy to
OL,14,Fgive up on days like this.
OL,16,F"I just think of Rita, and so many
OL,17,Fother amazing people who have lost
OL,18,Ftheir lives to bowel cancer.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@JO]uD@WOUxD@AOU
