OL,6,F"This will end, but that didn't. And
OL,7,Fthat just keeps me going, you know?
OL,8,FAnd it gets me to the top."
OL,10,FHis climbs are all about raising money
OL,11,Fand awareness for bowel cancer, now
OL,12,Fthe world's second deadliest type of
OL,13,Fcancer. Chris is determined to use the
OL,14,Fmountain to get people talking and
OL,15,Ftested.
OL,17,F"If you're over 50, you get a free
OL,18,Fscreening test every two years," he
OL,19,Fsays.
