OL,3,C'I just think of Rita': Man climbs Pen
OL,4,Cy Fan over 600 times in wife's memory
OL,6,F"I really, really urge people to do
OL,7,Fthat. If you catch the illness early,
OL,8,Fin over 95% of cases you will recover
OL,9,Ffrom it. Now that, for me, is a
OL,10,Fmountain worth summiting."
OL,12,FTowards the top, we pass two couples
OL,13,Fwho tell us the conditions forced them
OL,14,Fto turn back before the summit. Chris
OL,15,Fassures me we'll be fine.
OL,17,FAt the top of the near 3,000 foot
OL,18,Fmountain, he says he often gets
OL,19,Femotional here. Today, though, he's
OL,20,Fsimply exhilarated.
