OL,3,C'I just think of Rita': Man climbs Pen
OL,4,Cy Fan over 600 times in wife's memory
OL,6,F"It never gets boring," he says.
OL,8,FAs we head back down to get warm and
OL,9,Fdry, Chris turns into the wind and
OL,10,Fstarts the climb again, thinking of
OL,11,Fhis late wife.
OL,13,F"I know Rita would want me to enjoy
OL,14,Fevery single day and live life to the
OL,15,Fmax," he says. "That's what I'm trying
OL,16,Fto do. I'm privileged to be able to do
OL,17,Fthat."
